title: Junior Path
text: Cyber Trace’s Junior Path is a beginner-friendly path dedicated to our dear members. Each session of this path consists of an introduction to one of the numerous sub-domains of cyber security in addition to a mini-workshop helping them apply what they’ve just learnt.

title: Senior Path
text: Cyber Trace’s Senior Path is a path dedicated to the amateurs of cyber security. Within the sessions of this path, we discuss in-depth, one specific, delicate and very interesting concept of cyber security.
